SPIM
---------------------------

Spim - Variation of spam, aimed at users of instant messaging services. 

Why Spim is Prevalent?
   * Most IM Systems Provide DIRECTORIES
   * Spim can be sent
      - Benign Spim: ADs
      - Malicious Spim: Malware, can perpetuate a bot

Protection Against Spim - These will reduce spim fairly dramatically 
   * Use a Whitelist: List of users from which they choose to allow
   * Use an IM Blocker: 